  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Flights from Bristol</h2>
<p>Are you searching for holidays from Bristol? Travel to your dream European destination with the ease of flights departing directly from Bristol airport. Whether you crave the glistening lakes of Italy, the awe-inspiring landscapes of the Austrian Alps, or the cultural riches of Slovenia and Switzerland, we have you fully covered.</p>
<p><img style="width: 853px; height: 457px;" src="/media/13097453/portofino-1.jpg?width=853&amp;height=457&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/23bf40c025754b459500204bf0676173" /></p>
<p>We take care of everything for your holiday. <strong>Flights, hotel, and stress-free transfers are all included in our package holidays</strong>. Forget about travel worries, we’ll handle all of the details so you can focus on making unforgettable memories</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/f23d2b62232e4404a3831a9510eff1e0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f23d2b62232e4404a3831a9510eff1e0}" title="From Bristol" class="c-btn">View holidays from Bristol</a></p>
<p> </p>
<h2>Our Bristol Airport Destinations</h2>
<div>Europe’s blue skies are waiting. Get ready for an unforgettable holiday, where culture, delicious food, and stunning scenery await. Explore our holidays from Bristol and get ready for an incredible experience in the great outdoors.</div>
<div>
