<p><a name="Italy"></a></p>
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy Holidays From Bristol</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 863px; height: 463px;" src="/media/13096405/merano-1.jpg?width=863&amp;height=463&amp;mode=max" alt="Merano holidays from Birmingham" data-udi="umb://media/1c8b8df7d2dd49ddbd2a0b7ee4673000" /></p>
<p>Italy is a treasure trove of natural and historical marvels, from the stunning cliffs of the Amalfi Coast to the beauty of the Dolomite mountains. And with our holidays from Bristol, Italy’s wonders are simply a flight away. Step into the glorious Mediterranean sun and get ready to unlock the secrets of the famous Dolce Vita lifestyle.</p>
<h3>Our Italy Resorts</h3>
<p>Discover these beautiful Italian resorts, easily accessible with flights from Bristol.</p>
